          <svg class="w-2 h-2 text-white" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path d="M8 9a3 3 0 100-6 3 3 0 000 6zM8 11a6 6 0 016 6H2a6 6 0 016-6zM16 7a1 1 0 10-2 0v1h-1a1 1 0 100 2h1v1a1 1 0 102 0v-1h1a1 1 0 100-2h-1V7z"/></svg>
